column3: 2015 tambree ""tammy"" l. smiddy 41 of leitchfield passed away on monday june 8
column4: 2015 at twin lake regional medical center. she was preceded in death her mother sheila smiddy. she is survived by her children allexxis sinkhorn (aaron) of louisville
column6: mikayla wholney of louisville and rayna; her father larry smiddy (nora) of leitchfield; her sister angela smiddy of louisville and her grand daughter chelsea blanford. the family has chosen cremation with a memorial service to take place at a later date. online condolences to the family may be made at maramanbillings. com
